window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The <b>Ultimate Clean &amp; Wholesome Mega Christmas Box Set</b> from bestselling and Kindle All-Star authors <b>Katie Wyatt, Kat Carson, Ellen Anderson, and Ada Oakley!</b></p><p>Step into a world of faith, hope, and frontier courage in this <b>extraordinary 32-book Christmas collection</b>, featuring <b>8 complete Mail Order Bride series &amp; Historical Christian Western Romance </b> filled with sweet romance, heartfelt miracles, and the true meaning of love.</p><p>Travel back to the <b>1800s American frontier</b>—where life was hard, but hearts were strong, and faith was the light that guided every soul through the coldest winters. These stories are packed with <b>inspiring heroines</b>, <b>godly heroes</b>, <b>family bonds</b>, <b>second chances</b>, and plenty of <b>Christmas cheer</b> to warm your heart from the inside out.</p><p>From snow-covered small towns to bustling frontier settlements, you’ll meet brave young women who journey west as Mail Order Brides—each one chasing love, redemption, and the life God has called her to live. Along the way, they’ll face hardship, danger, and doubt—but also experience the blessings of faith, forgiveness, and everlasting love.</p><p>- <b>Clean. Wholesome. Faith-filled. Romantic.</b><br>- <b>Perfect for cozy nights, hot cocoa, and Christmas lights!</b><br>- <b>32 inspiring tales of love, laughter, and miracles—all in one breathtaking collection.</b></p><p>Each story captures the heart of what Christmas truly means: love born of faith, joy that conquers sorrow, and miracles that still shine bright on the Western frontier.</p><p><b>This is the Christmas collection you’ll cherish all year long!</b></p><b>Included in this one of kind collection…</b><br><b>Christmas Glory Bound Frontier Mail Order Bride Romance</b><br>Book 1 Holly's Hope<br>Book 2 Daphne’s Dream<br>Book 3 Heather’s Heart<br>Book 4 Camelia’s Courage<br>Book 5 Jasmine’s Faith<br><b>Christmas In Red Rock</b><br>Books 1 Catching Christmas Spirit<br>Books 2 The Spark of Christmas<br>Books 3 Seeing Christmas Spirit<br>Books 4 Christmas Spirit Returns<p><b>Frontier family Christmas love is THREE-novels, a series full of love, and the joys of the season!</b><br>Book 1 Two are Better than One<br>Book 2 Love One Another<br>Book 3 Love is Patient, Love is Kind</p><p><b>Mail Order Bride Christmas Miracles Romance</b><br>Book 1 Leigh's Love<br>Book 2 Melanie's Miracle<br>Book 3 Felicity's Folly<br>Book 4 Elise's Elation<br><b>Frontier Christmas Brides and Babies Series</b><br>Book 1: Sally’s Christmas<br>Book 2: Amelia’s Christmas<br>Book 3: Jenny’s Christmas<br>Book 4: Margaret Christmas<br>Book 5: Jane Brown’s Christmas<br>Book 6: Bessie’s Christmas</p><p><b>Christmas Cowboys Holiday Romance Series : THREE-novels,</b><br>Book 1: Mail Order, Maybe?<br>Book 2: The Christmas that Almost Wasn’t and the Miracle that Saved it All<br>Book 3: love and forgiveness</p><b>Mail Order Bride Holiday Romance</b><br>Book 1 Jasmine's Grace<br>Book 2 Heather's Heart<br>Book 3 Julie's Courage<br>Book 4 Charlotte's Serenade<p><b>Mallory's Miracle Christmas Complete Series</b><br>Book 1 Clara's Love<br>Book 2 Martha's Courage<br>Book 3 Emma's Reward</p><h4>Katie Wyatt’s Clean and Wholesome novelette American Mail Order Bride Historical Western box set romance series is enjoyable for all ages.</h4>"; 
